These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, mauve
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
2. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person who likes grey##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Color      | grey  | mauve   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Pet         | frog | rabbit |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the nigerian##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Beverage   | tea | soy-milk  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Nationality     | dutch   | nigerian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
There 2 different types of food: banana, lime
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person eating lime is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Sport    | rugby     | lacrosse |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Food         | banana         | lime        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

