.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, sailing
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
City: liverpool, paris
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person traveling to paris is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Sport          | sailing   | climbing  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| City   | liverpool  | paris         |

