1. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
