.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
City: san-francisco, paris
2 different games are played: bridge, poker
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| City         | paris        | san-francisco |
| Game         | bridge          | poker     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 